STATE
v.
Arthur O. ARMSTRONG. No. 232P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2006. Patricia A. Duffy, Assistant Attorney General, C. Colon Willoughby, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 12th day of July 2006 by Defendant for "Petition for Rehearing":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 17th day of August 2006."
